## Scope and Method

This inventory is based on the repo structure, key `README` files, package manifests, Netlify functions, shared JS, and the app/platform HTML surfaces themselves.

I separated items into:

- real products with meaningful implementation
- partial products or front-end-heavy shells
- sales/demo/platform concept pages
- confirmed stubs, placeholders, or link-quality issues

